metadata.name: Searching for Connection
metadata.description:
A family sits inside waiting for the blizzard to pass on a cold winters night. Walking around in the snow at night has become a meditative and healing process for me. Walking through this neighborhood in Minnesota during the blizzard, this scene caught my eye when I saw the American flag hanging out front. 

Edition: 1 of 1

Artist: Tyler James
